The paper discusses the need for explainable AI systems in the medical domain, which falls under the category of AI and machine learning (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning approaches (cs.LG) and focuses on three sources of data: images (cs.CV), *omics data (cs.CY), and text (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses legal and privacy aspects, which could fall under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). However, since the focus is on explainable AI in the medical domain, cs.CR is less likely to be a relevant sub-category.
